Description: Label printer GUI for Brother QL-700
 A user-friendly GUI application for printing labels with QR codes
 on Brother QL-700 label printers. Supports single label printing,
 batch mode, and text-only labels.
 .
 Features:
  - QR + Text labels: Print labels with QR codes and text
  - Batch mode: Print up to 10 labels in one batch
  - Text Only: Print centered text-only labels without QR codes
  - Preview before printing
  - Support for 29mm, 38mm, 50mm, and 62mm continuous tape
  - Customizable fonts and sizes
